content.html: “Oh shit, we’ve got no plan. We haven’t thought about it. I didn’t think it would happen. Holy crap, what will we do?” A quote attributed to Boris Johnson on the morning after Leave won the EU referendum, from Seldon and Newell’s new book on Johnson.
content.value:
“Oh shit, we’ve got no plan. We haven’t thought about it. I didn’t think it would happen. Holy crap, what will we do?”

A quote attributed to Boris Johnson on the morning after Leave won the EU referendum, from Seldon and Newell’s new book on Johnson.
